cross-country train in southern Pakistan on Sunday, killing 26
people. PAKISTAN-TRAIN BOMB. Lead has moved.
	   JAKARTA, Indonesia _ Indonesia's ex-President Suharto turns 77
on Monday, but there'll be no celebration for the man who last
month surrendered his 32-year iron grip over the nation.
INDONESIA-SUHARTO'S BIRTHDAY. Has moved. By Geoff Spencer.
	   BEIRUT, Lebanon _ Authorities trying to maintain Beirut's
