municipal elections. LEBANON-ELECTIONS. Has moved. By Hussein
Dakroub. AP Photo BEI101. Polls close at 1600 GMT. First results
expected by 2100 GMT.
	   FRANKFURT, Germany _ Rescue workers probe four meters (yards)
