endorse ways to combat trafficking, curb demand and strengthen
global cooperation in the fight against drugs. UN-DRUG SUMMIT. Has
moved. By Robert H. Reid.
	   BANGKOK, Thailand _ Thailand has no team in the World Cup and
has struggled to recover from a region-wide economic crisis, but
