<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Sports-Golf-English Open-Scores </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   WARE, England (AP) _ Final scores Sunday after the fourth round
of the English Open at the par-72, 7,016-yard Marriott Hanbury
Manor course:
