<SLUG> HOTLINE-SERVICE sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Hotline service for crisis victims, JAKARTA POST
</HEADLINE>
Hotline service for crisis victims, JAKARTA POST &QL; 
   June 06, 1998
   JAKARTA POST
