	   CHITTAGONG, June 6: The Chittagong Stock Exchange experienced a
bullish trend in its trading on the beginning of the week today
with significant rise in the price index.
	   The All Securities Price Index at the countries second bourse
increased by 23.89 points or 7.97 per cent to 323.37 points from
Thursday's 299.48 points.
