<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Eritrea-Ethiopia, 5th Ld,0295 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Eritreans brace for more Ethiopian warplane attacks
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: UPDATES 8th graf with Rice back in United States. PICKS UP
10th graf pvs: The proposal calls ... &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos ASM101-103 &QL; 
 &UR; By KARIN DAVIES &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
