<SLUG> BC-Eritrea-Ethiopia, 7th Ld,0455 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Eritreans brace for more Ethiopian warplane attacks
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: CORRECTS 15th graf to ``Isaias'' sted ``Afwerki'' &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photos ASM101-103 &QL; 
 &UR; By KARIN DAVIES &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

